{"tid":2219779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：環球經濟深度衰退，香港須調整定位和策略，向新移民派錢一萬，不再推保就業第3期","createTime":"2020-09-27T06:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T06:40:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4697d96c0ea2c8cb7a1bd8bce211186bad0cc6","tid":2219779,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551877-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551877-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0tT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=d20260ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551877-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=91a567e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551877-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波說，本港新型肺炎第三波疫情近日大致受控，但歐洲疫情出現急劇反彈，情況令人憂慮；環球經濟陷入深度衰退，香港要鞏固既有優勢，調整定位和策略。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗就呼籲市民，在國慶及中秋節長假期做好防疫措施，當局會密切注視疫情發展，並爭取早日落實粵港澳健康碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551879-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551879-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0tT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=7beff078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551879-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9737bc97\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551879-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n關愛基金向低收入家庭新來港定居人士，發放1萬元津貼，合資格人士今日可到17間中國銀行分行遞交申請表或上網申請。<br />\n<br />\n有市民早上8時已在銀行外等候交表，有申請人說，感謝政府支援，不過亦有人批評計劃來得太遲。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光到深水埗中銀分行視察，逗留半小時後離開。"},{"pid":"d145ddd69571cdd89733ff06fad3f406bcac424c","tid":2219779,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"經濟衰退前: 環球經濟不明朗，唔派錢<br />\n經濟衰退時: 環球經濟好疲弱，唔派錢"}]}